title: Beyond the Horror: 1984 Episode 7
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: This is very off topic, but I have to vent. Black Friday was yesterday, and I know that a fair number of people were killed on the Walmart properties and associated parking lots. Their souls are trapped there now, doomed to wander during sales but never able to buy anything. Or they are forced to be trampled again during the sales. I have a real spell book that's a couple hundred years old, but I think there's no power strong enough to free them.
Why would u put this out two weeks after ahs is over ???
